snippet.textDisplay:
Let's not be like people on the USA!!! Let's come together and United no matter of your political affiliation. I am not a liberal supporter but I recognize that this crisis would be very challenging for any government or president.

Let's comply with our health officials and government, don't do it for the party that is asking to do your part, let's do it for eachother, for our loved ones and for the thousands of healthcare workers who literally risk their lives to fight this pandemic.

We are Canadians, not Americans. Let's stop pointing fingers and look for someone to blame, that is so American. Instead let's support our Federal and Provincial governments, no matter what party they represent, because today they are one party, a party that we all count on and look up to.

As a Canadian I want to say I love you all, no matter where in Canada you are, i pray for every single one of you and your families as i do for our leaders who are faced with most challenging situation since World War II, let's be there for eachother and for time being put politics aside.
